BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Pakistan♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Plot No. 02, Sector W-59, Embassy District; PO Box 846&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +971 4 397 3600 &lt;/bdi&gt; , &lt;span class="tel"&gt;&lt;span class="type"&gt;fax&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;bdi class="value listing-fax"&gt; +971 4 397 1975 &lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/span&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Consular services are in &lt;a href="http%3A//www.mofa.gov.pk/dubai/"&gt;Dubai&lt;/a&gt; at Umm Hurair One, Khalid Bin Waleed Road, Bur Dubai,&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
