</ul>
<h2>Go next</h2>

<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡&lt;a href="Dubai"&gt;Dubai&lt;/a&gt; ♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;an hour and a half drive down the highway&lt;/bdi&gt;).&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡&lt;a href="Al%20Ain"&gt;Al Ain&lt;/a&gt; ♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;just 90 minutes away&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The UAE's largest oasis.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
