BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Hotel Restaurant La Rose Du Sable♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Kasbah Ait Benhaddou, Morocco&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +212 5 24 89 00 22 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Clean, comfortable rooms. Great food.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
