BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Bangor%20%28Maine%29"&gt;Bangor&lt;/a&gt;, ME 50 miles, 1 hour
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Portland%20%28Maine%29"&gt;Portland&lt;/a&gt;, ME 161 miles, 3.5 hours
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Kittery"&gt;Kittery&lt;/a&gt;, ME 211 miles, 4.5 hours
