<h2>Connect</h2>
This is commuterland for Manchester, so 4G / Wifi mobile signal is good.

<h2>Go next</h2>

A few miles north of Accrington, the River Ribble flows west out of scenic dales and hills. The closest area is ♡❤♡Pendle Hill♡❤♡, brooding above &lt;a href="Clitheroe"&gt;Clitheroe&lt;/a&gt;.

The upland north of the Ribble is ♡❤♡The &lt;a href="Forest%20of%20Bowland"&gt;Forest of Bowland&lt;/a&gt;♡❤♡ Area of Outstanding Natural Beauty. Further upstream lies the ♡❤♡&lt;a href="Yorkshire%20Dales"&gt;Yorkshire Dales&lt;/a&gt; National Park♡❤♡, usually accessed via &lt;a href="Skipton"&gt;Skipton&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Settle"&gt;Settle&lt;/a&gt; or Ingleton.

