BULLET::::- Otherwise it's back to the main road for routes towards &lt;a href="Ullapool"&gt;Ullapool&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="Inverness"&gt;Inverness&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="Durness"&gt;Durness&lt;/a&gt; on the north coast.
</ul>
 


