<h2>&lt;a href="Ghana"&gt;Ghana&lt;/a&gt;</h2>

<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Ada%20%28Ghana%29"&gt;Ada (Ghana)&lt;/a&gt; - A place in the southeast of Ghana.

