<doc id="188" url="https://en.wikivoyage.org/wiki?curid=188" title="Ada (Ohio)">
<h1>Ada (Ohio)</h1>
&lt;templatestyles src="Pagebanner/styles.css"/&gt;
♡❤♡The Village of Ada♡❤♡ is a college town in &lt;a href="Northwest%20Ohio"&gt;Northwest Ohio&lt;/a&gt;.

<h2>Get in</h2>
SR235 becomes the main street of ADA. Ada is just south of US30

<h2>Get around</h2>
The village of Ada is fairly small. Having a car or bicycle is ideal, but going on foot isn't a bad option.

<h2>See</h2>

<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q1683585"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Ohio Northern University♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;A private university with interesting architecture.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;span class="listing-sister-icons"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Elzay Gallery of Art♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +1 419-772-2160 &lt;/bdi&gt; , &lt;abbr title="email" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;✉&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;span class="email listing-email"&gt; art@onu.edu &lt;/span&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-hours"&gt;1PM-4:30PM&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-price"&gt;Free&lt;/bdi&gt;.&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡English Chapel♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The church of Ohio Northern University.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡The Tundra♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The giant green commons that cuts across the campus core. It's good for a pleasant walk.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt;&lt;span id="Q4678287"&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Train Station♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;While no longer used for passenger service, the train station still stands.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;span class="listing-sister-icons"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;

