<h2>Eat</h2>
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡El Campo♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;204 N Main St&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +1 419 634-0009 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;&lt;a href="Mexican_cuisine"&gt;Mexican&lt;/a&gt; food. Has a &lt;a href="Travel_as_a_vegetarian"&gt;vegetarian&lt;/a&gt; section on its menu.
</ul>
 &lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt; 
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Northern On Main♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="nickname listing-alt"&gt;NOM&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Coffeehouse. Sandwichs, salads, pastries...&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Viva María's♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;124 E Buckeye St&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +1 567-940-8482 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Run by an Italian immigrant. Known for their white pizza. Sells pizza, strombolis, calzones, pasta, and wings.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
