BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Adams%20County%20%28Colorado%29"&gt;Adams County (Colorado)&lt;/a&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;a href="Adams%20County%20%28Idaho%29"&gt;Adams County (Idaho)&lt;/a&gt;
