<h3>Splurge</h3>
<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Aladdin restaurant♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Zimbabwe St, off Bole Rd, Rwanda area, Bole subcity&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;near Japan Embassy&lt;/bdi&gt;), &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +251 11 661 4109, +251 11 861 7731, +251 92 992 3492 &lt;/bdi&gt; , &lt;abbr title="email" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;✉&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;span class="email listing-email"&gt; aladdinrestaurantplc@gmail.com &lt;/span&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Armenian and Mediterranean restaurant. Serves fine Middle-Eastern food, various mezzes including a gorgeous tabbouleh. In quiet atmosphere, perfect for a romantic diner. Very expensive but authentic and delicious.&lt;/bdi&gt; &lt;bdi class="note listing-price"&gt;290&amp;nbsp;birr&lt;/bdi&gt;.&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Castellis in Piazza♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Churchill St/Piazza area&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Top Italian restaurant here since 1942. With famous guests such as Angelina Jolie and Brad Pitt there is a reason that Castelli's manages to attract such a crowd. This is where the Italian embassy staff goes to eat. Amazing food, amazing desserts, call for a reservation or risk disappointment, even at lunch time, as this is a trendy place to be seen.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Fisherman Restaurant♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Mickey Leland St&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;near Atlas Hotel&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;A half-Chinese, half-Tibetan restaurant specialising in seafood and serving an excellent range of Asian cuisine.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
