BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Sangam Restaurant♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Bole Rd&lt;/bdi&gt;. &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Excellent place for Indian food and sweets, often used by the Indian embassy. Loads of variety with rice, chapati, naan. Pleasant atmosphere and price is very good.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Top View Restaurant♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Megenagna area, above the Diaspora Roundabout, crossing of Ring Rd with Fikre mariam Aba Techan St&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;near the Israeli embassy&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Very good food but can be expensive for dinner. But the view is not so "top" since new buildings.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
