BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Lemon3lodge♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Kirkwood&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +27 42 230-1653 &lt;/bdi&gt; , &lt;abbr title="email" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;✉&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;span class="email listing-email"&gt; Info@lemon3lodge.co.za &lt;/span&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The rooms are all air-conditioned with double beds and en suite bathrooms. The rooms have all amenities such as a hairdryer, shampoos and lotions, as well as wireless internet on arrangement. The guest lounge has a television with DSTV and a DVD player. Breakfast is usually served 7AM-9:30AM.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
