BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Dumas House♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;11 Druids Avenue, Mount Barker&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +61 417 445 663 &lt;/bdi&gt; , &lt;abbr title="email" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;✉&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;span class="email listing-email"&gt; enquiries@dumashouse.com &lt;/span&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The former residence of Mr Charles Dumas and his family is available as self-contained accommodation.&lt;/bdi&gt; &lt;bdi class="note listing-price"&gt;M-Th $220-245, F-Su $246-265&lt;/bdi&gt;.&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Old Mill Hahndorf♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;98 Main Street, Hahndorf&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;abbr title="phone" style="text-decoration:none"&gt;☏&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;bdi class="tel listing-phone"&gt; +61 8 8388 7888 &lt;/bdi&gt; . &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;A beautiful old building on Hahndorf's Main Street. Very comfortable accommodation, with a sumptuous buffet dinner.&lt;/bdi&gt; &lt;bdi class="note listing-price"&gt;From $75&lt;/bdi&gt;.&lt;/bdi&gt;

</ul>
<h2>Go next</h2>

It is easy to drive north to &lt;a href="Barossa%20Valley"&gt;Barossa Valley&lt;/a&gt; or south to &lt;a href="McLaren%20Vale"&gt;McLaren Vale&lt;/a&gt; to visit other wonderful wine region, or south to the ocean and the Murray and the towns of &lt;a href="Victor%20Harbor"&gt;Victor Harbor&lt;/a&gt; and &lt;a href="Goolwa"&gt;Goolwa&lt;/a&gt;.

