<h2>See</h2>

<ul>
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Parthasarathy Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;near the Private Bus Stand&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The most important temple in town.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Trichenamangalam Mahadevar Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;10&amp;nbsp;kilometers away at Peringanad&lt;/bdi&gt;).&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Sree Dharma Sastha Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;5&amp;nbsp;kilometers away at Chenampalil&lt;/bdi&gt;).&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Peedikayil Devi Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Pannivizha&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;A wonderful temple with century old traditions.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Sree Mahadevar Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Pannivizha&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;One of the rare Dekshinamoorthy temples with century old traditions.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Ezhamkulam Devi Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;5&amp;nbsp;km from Adoor Town&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Famous for "Garudan Thookam and Kettukazhcha" that takes place as a part of the annual Kumbhabharani Festival.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Ammummakavu Devi Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="nickname listing-alt"&gt;Chiranickal&lt;/bdi&gt;), &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Parakode North - Chiranickal&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;5&amp;nbsp;km from Adoor Town&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;Ammummakavu is the Propitiating Mother Goddess.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Kodumon Palliyara Devi Temple (Chilanthi Ambalam)♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;1.5&amp;nbsp;km East of Kodumon Jn:&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;8&amp;nbsp;km from Adoor Town&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;The water of the Chilanthikinar (Well) on the premises of this temple is believed to cure skin diseases.&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Orippurathu Bhagavathi Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt;, &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Orippuram Thattayil&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Adoor - Thumpamon Road Take diversion from Keerukuzhy Jn.&lt;/bdi&gt;). &lt;bdi class="note listing-content"&gt;8&amp;nbsp;KM from Adoor Town Easy Access By road&lt;/bdi&gt;&lt;/bdi&gt;
BULLET::::- &lt;bdi class="vcard"&gt; &lt;bdi class="listing-name"&gt;♡❤♡Bhagavatikunnu Devi Temple♡❤♡&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="nickname listing-alt"&gt;Elamannoor Bhoothamkara&lt;/bdi&gt;), &lt;bdi class="adr listing-address street-address"&gt;Durga Temple&lt;/bdi&gt; (&lt;bdi class="listing-directions" style="font-style: italic;"&gt;Temple&lt;/bdi&gt;).&lt;/bdi&gt;

